org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.FailurePropagation

Interface FPTCSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FI4FASpecification
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FI4FASpecificationImpl, FPTCSpecificationImpl

    public interface FPTCSpecification
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'FPTC Specification'. this allows to work with FPTC at instance level by using composite diagrams. It allows to decorate ports of the parts. attribute 'failure' is deprecated, use 'failureModes'

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Comment
    • Failure
    • Part With Port
    • Failure Mode
    See Also:
    FailurePropagationPackage.getFPTCSpecification()
